@*
    Smart Link SDK — renders click-to-edit overlays on elements decorated with
    data-kontent-item-id / data-kontent-element-codename / data-kontent-component-id.

    The SDK reads data-kontent-environment-id and data-kontent-language-codename from an ancestor
    (_Layout.cshtml sets them on <body>), so no further configuration is needed here.

    Version is pinned: v4 used data-kontent-project-id; v5 renamed it to data-kontent-environment-id.
    Activation: auto-activates inside the Kontent.ai Studio Web Spotlight iframe; outside the iframe,
    append ?ksl-enabled to the URL.
*@
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@@kontent-ai/smart-link@@5/dist/bundles/kontent-smart-link.min.js"></script>
<script>
    kontentSmartLink.KontentSmartLink.initializeOnLoad();
</script>
